title: GORGEOUS UNIT IN PARAMOUNT WORLD!
posting_body: ['Welcome to the best deal in all of Paramount Miami for a brand new never lived in corner unit 3bed/4bath + den with private elevator and foyer.', 'Features include: 10 ft high ceilings, white/marble flooring, Bosch and Sub Zero appliances, marble backsplash in the kitchen, large den that can be used as a dining area or 4th bedroom, custom built in closets, sheer blinds in the living room and black out in all bedrooms, huge terrace, laundry room with full washer/dryer, huge walk in closet in the master, an extra large closet in the den area and much more.', 'High end finishes complete the unit with huge white quartz island kitchen and much more.', 'Amenities include: tennis, basketball, racquetball, soccer, 5 pools, roof top pool, classes, bbq and much more.', 'All units Year Lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher, proof of income 2.5 times greater than rent price required, first + last + security deposit to move in.', 'please TEXT :', 'show contact info']
